  "texts": [
    "Transformation of single site mutants.",
    "96-well deep-well plates are shaken in an INFORS HT Multitron Shaker in all instances.",
    "The assembly products obtained were used to transform T7 Express Competent E. coli (High Efficency) cells (NEB, Ipswich, MA) following the recommended protocol.",
    "Upon heat-shock transformation, mixtures were recovered in 0.4 mL Luria-Bertani medium (LB) (Research Products Int.",
    "), after which the cells were incubated at 37 °C with shaking at 220 rpm for 30 min before being plated on LB-agar plates with 100 μg/mL ampicillin (LB-amp agar plates)."
